They got everything here from fish food to frogs to filters.

You can get accessories here with ornaments and other consumables here. Your one stop shop for aquatic hobbies.

What they don’t have is credit card payments. It’s a simple business with easy payment and honest prices to suit all your needs.

text.text:
As a beginner fish hobbyist, the uncle operating the shop help me with my "cloudy" tank problem and gave good advise. He goes beyond and how big my tank was and also provide guidance on the fish that can be mix which are more peaceful Vs those which are more aggressive in nature.

Also can see that the items in the shop are sold are reasonable rates. Highly recommend this shop if you are checking out on aquarium related stuff.

text.text:
Good helpful people here can give you advice on hardwares or simple set up ideas for starters.

Polyart does setup and maintenance of tanks or pond at your home. They can share pointers for your enjoyment with fishes that'll interact well with you.

Food for fishes, plants or water additives for conditioning of both marine and freshwater setups. They have it all here.

They are very friendly and do provide discounts or extended warranty which is rare for most aquarium shops.

I'm going to start my new aquaculture tank this week. Pop-in, I might see you there too. Relax & Enjoy the simplicity of adding another dimension to our home!
